# cob-chart

This component uses [Vega](https://vega.github.io/vega/) and [VegaLite](https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/) to render charts on a boston.gov page.

More documentation can be found in the [Digital Team's GitBook space](https://docs.boston.gov/digital/projects/charts-on-boston.gov).
